textAfterTable: More Less Payment methods accepted Wire transfer Portfolio Sample translations submitted: 2 English to Malay: Telecommunications industry Source text - English The telecommunications industry is responsible for radio, television, voice communications, and broadband services. The growth and innovation of the telecom industry has enabled people to communicate across the globe and access endless amounts of information over the internet. Broadband services are becoming faster and easier to access with fiber optic networks and wireless services. Many of the major telecom companies have merged over the last 10 years in order to offer massive product and service portfolios. These new technologies and growth through mergers are enabling these companies to find new revenue sources and growth opportunities in a mostly mature market.
